{"tid":1139646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"688bf5d176908d35ab1af6c512001f599651be79","tid":1139646,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190505/20671015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F20671015&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=913d3378\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F20671015&h=2e008a06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190505/20671015</a><br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190505/large/a0803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190505%2Flarge%2Fa0803a.gif&h=29dc84fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「中國大陸的每一個政治運動傷及百姓都以數十萬計，乃至數百萬、上千萬。這個龐大的社會群體性回顧，都屬於共同記憶。由於執政者長期查禁和親歷者大部份死去，原本的『共同記憶』就成了問題&hellip;&hellip;我們這個民族的『共同記憶』正在流失，正在有效地、迅速地流失。掐指算來，距離天安門廣場那個血色夜晚，還不足二十年，而我們的年輕人已茫然不知了。這是愚昧瘠貧土壤培育出來的碩大無比的時代苦果，讓今天的每一個人都來咀嚼吞嚥它。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;中國作家章詒和寫於2007年6至8月．北京  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【採訪手記】倫敦六四研討會的「安全須知」<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【採訪手記】倫敦六四研討會的「安全須知」<br />\n<br />\n【採訪手記】倫敦六四研討會的「安全須知」<br />\n延續獨立思考火種流亡學者 誓翻黑歷史的牆"}]}